			</div>
			<div class="information-description">
				<p>
					There are several text editing programs that programers use to write HTML, CSS, Javascript, ect. Each of them have their own advantages and disadvantages. When writing these notes, I am using Sublime Text 2.
				</p>
				<p>
					<a href="https://www.udacity.com/course/viewer#!/c-nd000/l-4137489485/m-3521349459">This Page</a> helps guide you to which text editor might be right for you.
